<html lang='es'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Tu acceso a GetInMotion</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto,
          'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b2b2b 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
      }
      .logo {
        height: 50px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .content {
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        border-left: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        border-right: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #2b2b2b;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .message {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }
      .credentials {
        margin: 30px 0;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      }
      .credentials-row {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #2b2b2b;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
      .credentials-value {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      }
      .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 35px 0;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #d4ff00;
        color: #2b2b2b;
        padding: 16px 40px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .expiry-notice {
        color: #999;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-top: 25px;
        font-style: italic;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f5f5f5;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 25px 20px;
        color: #888;
        font-size: 13px;
        border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      }
      .footer-emoji {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin: 0 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        {{#if logoUrl}}
          <img src='{{logoUrl}}' alt='GetInMotion' class='logo' />
        {{/if}}
        <h1>GetInMotion</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <div class='greeting'>¡Bienvenido, {{name}}! 🎉</div>
        <p class='message'>
          Tu cuenta en <strong>GetInMotion</strong> ha sido verificada. Estas son
          tus credenciales de acceso:
        </p>
        <div class='credentials'>
          <p class='credentials-row'>Correo:
            <span class='credentials-value'>{{email}}</span></p>
          <p class='credentials-row'>Contraseña:
            <span class='credentials-value'>{{password}}</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class='button-container'>
          <a href='{{loginUrl}}' class='button'>Iniciar sesión</a>
        </div>
        <p class='expiry-notice'>
          Por seguridad, te recomendamos cambiar esta contraseña después de
          iniciar sesión.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Con cariño desde Bogotá, Colombia
          <span class='footer-emoji'>🇨🇴</span></p>
        <p style='margin-top: 10px;'>GetInMotion © {{year}}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
